<p><a href="http://www.bjornhurri.com/steampunk-starwars-yoda/" target="_blank"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="alignleft" style="border:0;margin:0;" alt="" src="http://www.bjornhurri.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/02/Yoda_Hurri_Final.jpg" width="267" height="390" /></a>      <a href="http://www.bjornhurri.com/steampunk-starwars-luke-skywalker/" target="_blank"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="alignnone" alt="" src="http://www.bjornhurri.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/02/Luke_Hurri_Final.jpg" width="267" height="390" /></a></p>
